<lb n="0423b02" ed="T"/>薩羅<app source="0423013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>諾訖灑<app source="0423011" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>怛<note n="0423023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔羅〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423023"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><app source="0423011" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>邏<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note place="inline">上</note>
<lb n="0423b03" ed="T"/>野者<note n="0423024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＝去【甲】</note><app n="0423024"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">去</rdg></app>都地波阿<note place="inline">去引</note>路迦羅<note n="0423025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔野〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423025"><lem wit="【大】">野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline"><note n="0423026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝二合【甲】</note><app n="0423026"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0423b04" ed="T"/>他<note n="0423027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔努〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423027"><lem wit="【大】">努</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0423028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩底跛＝麼&CB03773;底【甲】</note><app n="0423028"><lem wit="【大】">摩底跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麼&CB03773;底</rdg></app>努摩底薩賓<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00135;佉<note place="inline">上</note>細娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0423b05" ed="T"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0423b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b0601"><note n="0423029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＝說【甲】</note><app n="0423029"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">說</rdg></app>此九曜息災大白衣觀音陀羅尼。若日月
<lb n="0423b07" ed="T"/>在人本命宮中。及五星在<note n="0423030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔本〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423030"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>命宮&CB00508;戰失度。
<lb n="0423b08" ed="T"/>可立大<note n="0423031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白衣＝息災&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0423031"><lem wit="【大】">白衣</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">息災</rdg></app>觀音或文殊八字熾盛光<note n="0423032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423032"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0423b09" ed="T"/>等道場。各依本法念誦。一切災難自然消
<lb n="0423b10" ed="T"/><note n="0423033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0423033"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">散也</rdg></app>。一切曜不吉祥誦此真言成能吉祥。</p>
<lb n="0423b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b1101">北斗七星真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0423b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b1201" type="dharani">唵颯跢曩而<note place="inline">齒</note>曩野伴惹<note n="0423034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密＋（惹）【甲】</note><app n="0423034"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">密惹</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">二合</note>染普他摩
<lb n="0423b13" ed="T"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>弭曩<note place="inline">名位</note><app source="0422010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>訖山婆&CB00085;都<app source="0422032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">莎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">娑&CB00085;</rdg></app><note n="0423035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423035"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b1401">若羅<note n="0423036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00264;＝曜【甲】</note><app n="0423036"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00264;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曜</rdg></app>計都暗行人本命星宮。須誦此北斗
<lb n="0423b15" ed="T"/>真言。一切如來說。破一切宿曜<note n="0423037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔障〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423037"><lem wit="【大】">障</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>吉祥。真
<lb n="0423b16" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0423b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b1701" type="dharani">唵薩羅&CB00085;諾剎怛<app source="0422010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>三<note n="0423038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【甲】</note><app n="0423038"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麼</rdg></app>曳室<app source="0423003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">哩</rdg></app>曳扇
<lb n="0423b18" ed="T"/>底迦<note n="0423039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔俱〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423039"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>嚕娑&CB00085;<note n="0423040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＝二合賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423040"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0423b1901">金剛<note n="0423041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宿＝大【甲】</note><app n="0423041"><lem wit="【大】">宿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>成就經。吉祥成就品<note n="0423042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曰＝云【甲】</note><app n="0423042"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">云</rdg></app>。我今宣說
<lb n="0423b20" ed="T"/>世間成就<note n="0423043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（最）＋妙【甲】</note><app n="0423043"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">最妙</rdg></app>祕法。如是諸曜運行虛空。若一
<lb n="0423b21" ed="T"/>若二三四五等。臨入眾生命宿對衝宿遷移
<lb n="0423b22" ed="T"/>宿大殺<note n="0423044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（宿）＋業【甲】</note><app n="0423044"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">宿業</rdg></app>宿安宿薄相宿奴婢宿。作諸厄害。
<lb n="0423b23" ed="T"/>四大惡曜。所謂火曜土曜羅&CB00264;計都最重眾
<lb n="0423b24" ed="T"/>生。是時修諸福業廣施<note n="0423045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仁慈＝慈仁【甲】</note><app n="0423045"><lem wit="【大】">仁慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慈仁</rdg></app>。或依文殊八字
<lb n="0423b25" ed="T"/>真言。<note n="0423046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">或＋（又）【甲】</note><app n="0423046"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或又</rdg></app>依熾盛光佛頂。或依被葉衣觀音。
<lb n="0423b26" ed="T"/>或依一字王佛頂。立<note n="0423047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝火【甲】</note><app n="0423047"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">火</rdg></app>息災護摩壇場。各
<lb n="0423b27" ed="T"/>依本法念誦供養。一切災難自然消滅。作成
<lb n="0423b28" ed="T"/>就法於心宿直日柳宿直日昴宿直日牛宿直
<lb n="0423b29" ed="T"/>日。不簡日月吉凶。但於此宿直日於一日之
<pb n="0423c" id="T21.1304.0423c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0423c01" ed="T"/>中。不食念誦滿一千八<note n="0423048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔十〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423048"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>遍。所有心願應時
<lb n="0423c02" ed="T"/>便<note n="0423049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">渴＝得【甲】</note><app n="0423049"><lem wit="【大】">渴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">得</rdg></app>大悉地。若厄難時。於本生日最<note n="0423050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（為）＋相【甲】</note><app n="0423050"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為相</rdg></app>應。
<lb n="0423c03" ed="T"/>若作木曜成就法者。月十六日最為相應。若
<lb n="0423c04" ed="T"/>作火曜成<note n="0423051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">就＝熟【甲】＊</note><app n="0423051"><lem wit="【大】">就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">熟</rdg></app>法者。即彼直日最為相應。若作
<lb n="0423c05" ed="T"/>土曜成<app source="0423051" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">熟</rdg></app>法者。每月七日最為相應。若作金
<lb n="0423c06" ed="T"/>曜成就法者。隨所見方平<note n="0423052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">旦＋（最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦）【甲】</note><app n="0423052"><lem wit="【大】">旦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">旦最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦</rdg></app><note n="0423053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">最為相應＝為勝【甲】</note><app n="0423053"><lem wit="【大】">最為相應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為勝</rdg></app>。若
<lb n="0423c07" ed="T"/>作水曜成就法者依水曜直日而作成就。若
<lb n="0423c08" ed="T"/>作羅&CB00264;計都法者。依本生<note n="0423054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（星）＋日【甲】</note><app n="0423054"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">星日</rdg></app>以為相應。若復
<lb n="0423c09" ed="T"/>供養本<note n="0423055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝星【甲】</note><app n="0423055"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">星</rdg></app>宿者。於本生年<note n="0423056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月＝日【甲】</note><app n="0423056"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">日</rdg></app>。若本生日而
<lb n="0423c10" ed="T"/>可取成就。若惡宿生每月供養。若三<note n="0423057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＋（五日）【甲】</note><app n="0423057"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">日五日</rdg></app>七日
<lb n="0423c11" ed="T"/>供<note n="0423058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">養＋（惡曜）【甲】</note><app n="0423058"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">養惡曜</rdg></app>直轉成吉祥直。祕勿令知<note n="0423059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">俗＋（人）【甲】</note><app n="0423059"><lem wit="【大】">俗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俗人</rdg></app>也<note n="0423060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書云康元二年二月晦日於覺洞院中寫之了觀尊二十二</note>。</p>
